Miscellaneous:
--------------

_060_fpsp_snan:
----------------
- documented in 3.5 of 060SP spec.
- Basic flow:
	exception taken ---> enter _060_fpsp_snan --|
						    |
            always exits through _060_real_snan <----

_060_fpsp_operr:
----------------
- documented in 3.5 of 060SP spec.
- Basic flow:
	exception taken ---> enter _060_fpsp_operr --|
						     |
           always exits through _060_real_operr <-----

_060_fpsp_dz:
----------------
