_060_fpsp_ovfl:
----------------
- documented in 3.4 of 060SP spec.
- Basic flow:
	exception taken ---> enter _060_fpsp_ovfl --|
						    |
            may exit through _060_real_inex     <---|
						 or |
            may exit through _060_real_ovfl     <---|
						 or |
            may exit through _060_fpsp_done     <---|

